~ star_cow_pasture_box
Pasture Box: [[Hi| Hello| Howdy]], your animals are hungry.
Pasture Box: Would you like to feed yours cows?
- Yes
	Marlow: Yeah! Lets feed my cows.
	do GameDialogueManager.action_feed_animals()
- No 
	Marlow: I don't need to feed them. Ihave enough milk.
=> END

